dishes.description: A classic salad with crisp romaine lettuce, parmesan cheese, and croutons, topped with tender grilled chicken. Dressed with a creamy Caesar dressing.
A medley of fresh vegetables saut√©ed in a savory sauce. Served with steamed rice for a fulfilling meal.
Creamy spaghetti combined with crispy pancetta and a hint of garlic. Topped with fresh parsley and grated parmesan cheese.
Fresh salmon fillet, seasoned and grilled to perfection. Served with lemon wedges and a side of asparagus.
Juicy and tender beef steak seasoned with herbs and grilled. Paired with roasted potatoes and a rich mushroom sauce.
A hearty vegetable patty served in a soft bun. Topped with fresh lettuce, tomato, and a tangy sauce.
Soft tortillas filled with grilled shrimp, fresh cabbage slaw, and a zesty lime sauce. A refreshing and tangy delight.
Tender lamb chops seasoned and grilled to perfection. Complemented with a mint sauce for a harmonious blend of flavors.
